# 此檔案定義在建置 Docker 映像檔時要排除的檔案和目錄
# 減少 build context 大小可以加速建置過程
#
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Dependencies
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
node_modules
npm-debug.log
yarn-debug.log
yarn-error.log
pnpm-debug.log
.npm
.yarn

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Next.js Build Output
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.next
.next/**
out
dist
build

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment Variables
# 警告：不要將真實的 .env 檔案打包進映像檔！
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.development
.env.development.local
.env.test
.env.test.local
.env.production
.env.production.local

# 僅保留 .env.example 作為範本參考
!.env.example

